wo%20organisations%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20A%20significant%20portion%20of%20his%20wealth%20has%20been%20set%20aside%20for%20his%20family%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20close%20associates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20of%20the%20late%20industrialist's%20other%20financial%20assets%2C%20including%20bank%20fixed%20deposits%2C%20financial%20instruments%20and%20physical%20possessions%20such%20as%20art%20and%20timepieces%2C%20estimated%20at%20Rs%20800%20crore%2C%20will%20be%20divided%20between%20his%20half-sisters%2C%20Shireen%20Jejeebhoy%20and%20Deanna%20Jejeebhoy%2C%20and%20Mohini%20M.%20Dutta%2C%20a%20former%20Tata%20Group%20employee%20who%20was%20close%20to%20Tata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETata's%20brother%2C%20Jimmy%20Naval%20Tata%2C%20will%20inherit%20a%20share%20of%20the%20family's%20Juhu%20bungalow%2C%20while%20close%20friend%20Mehli%20Mistry%20is%20set%20to%20receive%20the%20Alibaug%20property%20and%20his%20treasured%20collection%20of%20three%20firearms%2C%20which%20includes%20a%20.25-bore%20pistol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20includes%20a%20fourth%20codicil%2C%20which%20says%20that%20unlisted%20stocks%20and%20shares%2C%20as%20well%20as%20any%20assets%20not%20specifically%20detailed%20elsewhere%2C%20will%20be%20equally%20distributed%20between%20the%20Ratan%20Tata%20Endowment%20Foundation%20and%20the%20Ratan%20Tata%20Endowment%20Trust%2C%20according%20to%20court%20papers%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20probate%20process%2C%20the%20executors%20of%20Tata's%20will%20-%20lawyer%20Darius%20Kambatta%2C%20Mehli%20Mistry%2C%20and%20his%20sisters%20Shireen%20and%20Deanna%20Jejeebhoy%20-%20have%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court.%20The%20probate%20procedure%2C%20which%20confirms%20the%20authenticity%20of%20a%20will%20and%20grants%20the%20executors%20the%20authority%20to%20distribute%20the%20estate%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20around%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETata's%20will%20also%20ensures%20that%20his%20pets%20are%20cared%20for%20after%20his%20death.%20A%20sum%20of%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20has%20been%20earmarked%20for%20their%20care%2C%20with%20each%20pet%20receiving%20Rs%2030%2C000%20per%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETata's%20executive%20assistant%2C%20Shantanu%20Naidu%2C%20will%20have%20his%20student%20loan%20waived%2C%20while%20neighbour%20Jake%20Malite%20will%20also%20benefit%20from%20an%20interest-free%20education%20loan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECourt%20papers%20show%20that%20in%20addition%20to%20a%20cash%20balance%20of%20over%20Rs%204%20lakh%20and%20around%20Rs%20367%20crore%20held%20in%20local%20bank%20accounts%20and%20fixed%20deposits%2C%20Ratan%20Tata's%20foreign%20assets%20include%20Rs%2040%20crore%20worth%20of%20property%20in%20Seychelles%2C%20along%20with%20bank%20accounts%20at%20Wells%20Fargo%20and%20Morgan%20Stanley%2C%20and%20shares%20in%20Alcoa%20Corp%20and%20Howmet%20Aerospace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20asset%20list%20also%20includes%2065%20luxury%20watches%20from%20brands%20such%20as%20Bvlgari%2C%20Patek%20Philippe%2C%20Tissot%20and%20Audemars%20Piguet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETata's%20land%20holdings%20in%20Seychelles%20are%20to%20be%20transferred%20to%20RNT%20Associates%20Singapore%2C%20with%20instructions%20to%20protect%20the%20interests%20of%20shareholders%20R%20Venkatraman%20and%20Patrick%20McGoldrick%20in%20RNT%20Associates%20India%20and%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20Jimmy%20Tata%20will%20receive%20silverware%20and%20some%20jewellery%2C%20while%20also%20inheriting%20half%20of%20the%20Juhu%20property%2C%20which%20Ratan%20Tata%20inherited%20from%20his%20father%2C%20Naval%20H%20Tata.%20The%20remainder%20of%20the%20property%20will%20be%20shared%20by%20Simone%20Tata%20and%20Noel%20Tata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERatan%20Tata%20died%20on%20October%209%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743510120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fnij0qrbg_ratan-tata_625x300_28_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22http