riel%20Oluwasegun%20Olanrewaju%20Dies%20After%20Collapsing%20Mid-Bout%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Nigerian%20professional%20boxer%20Gabriel%20Oluwasegun%20%26quot%3BSuccess%26quot%3B%20Olanrewaju%20tragically%20died%20after%20collapsing%20during%20a%20fight%20in%20Ghana%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Fboxing%2Farticles%2Fcly1wyvz9qxo%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%20The%20former%20Nigerian%20and%20West%20African%20light-heavyweight%20champion%2C%20collapses%20onto%20the%20ropes%20in%20the%20third%20round-%20without%20taking%20a%20punch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2040-year-old%20boxer%20received%20first%20aid%20in%20the%20ring%20before%20being%20rushed%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20where%20he%20was%20pronounced%20dead%2030%20minutes%20after%20arrival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Ghana%20Boxing%20Authority%20(GBA)%2C%20Oluwasegun%20Olanrewaju%20stepped%20back%20and%20leaned%20against%20the%20ropes%20just%20seconds%20before%20the%20end%20of%20the%20third%20round%2C%20without%20taking%20a%20punch%20from%20his%20opponent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESensing%20distress%2C%20the%20referee%20stopped%20the%20fight%20and%20called%20for%20the%20ringside%20physician%2C%20who%2C%20along%20with%20paramedics%20from%20the%20National%20Ambulance%20Service%2C%20attempted%20to%20resuscitate%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GBA%20stated%20that%20Olanrewaju%20had%20been%20declared%20medically%20fit%20by%20the%20Nigeria%20Boxing%20Board%20Control%20(NBBC)%2C%20which%20had%20sanctioned%20and%20approved%20the%20fight.%20However%2C%20the%20NBBC%20later%20told%20The%20Punch%20that%20it%20had%20not%20authorized%20the%20specific%20bout%20in%20which%20he%20passed%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20Olanrewaju%20was%20initially%20scheduled%20to%20fight%20on%20Friday%20but%20was%20deemed%20overweight%20for%20the%20match.%20NBBC%20secretary%20Remi%20Aboderin%20told%20The%2