20seen%20outside%20a%20demolished%20house.%20Everyone%20is%20very%20disturbed%20by%20such%20visuals%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%20said%20as%20the%20court%20came%20down%20heavily%20against%20the%20authorities%2C%20calling%20the%20bulldozer%20action%20%26quot%3Binhuman%26quot%3B%20and%20ordering%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20compensation%20to%20each%20homeowner%20who%20approached%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20of%20Justice%20AS%20Oka%20and%20Justice%20Bhuyan%20slammed%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20for%20razing%20the%20homes%20of%20a%20lawyer%2C%20a%20professor%20and%20some%20others%20without%20following%20due%20procedure.%20Advocate%20Zulfiqar%20Haider%2C%20Professor%20Ali%20Ahmed%20and%20three%20others%20had%20told%20the%20court%20that%20they%20were%20given%20notices%20just%20one%20night%20before%20the%20bulldozer%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20representing%20the%20petitioners%20had%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20authorities%20mistakenly%20identified%20the%20land%20on%20which%20their%20homes%20were%20built%20as%20belonging%20to%20gangster%20Atiq%20Ahmed%2C%20who%20was%20murdered%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20pulled%20up%20the%20authorities%20for%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20demolition%20notices%20were%20served.%20While%20the%20State%20counsel%20said%20the%20notices%20were%20affixed%20at%20the%20properties%2C%20the%20court%20questioned%20why%20the%20notices%20were%20not%20sent%20by%20registered%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20cases%20shock%20our%20conscience.%20Residential%20premises%20of%20the%20appellants%20have%20been%20high%20handedly%20demolished%20in%20matter%20which%20we%20have%20discussed%20in%20detail%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%20in%20its%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20viral%20video%20the%20court%20referred%20to%20is%20from%20Ambedkar%20Nagar%20district%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20During%20a%20demolition%20action%20in%20Jalalpur%2C%20the%20girl%20was%20seen%20