ivate%20security%20team%20when%20said%20security%20team%20went%20to%20give%20access%20to%20Mr.%20Jackson%2C%26quot%3B%20DOGE%20wrote%20in%20an%20X%20post%20on%20March%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20taking%20office%20in%20January%2C%20Trump's%20administration%20has%20moved%20quickly%20to%20cull%20federal%20spending.%20Musk%20and%20DOGE%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-job-cuts-layoffs-highest-level-2020-covid-pandemic-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaid%20off%20thousands%20of%20federal%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarco-rubio-announces-official-end-of-most-usaid-programs-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshuttered%20foreign%20aid%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sparking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanagement-experts-musk-doge-case-study-bad-management-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efear%20and%20chaos%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20said%20at%20a%20cabinet%20meeting%20on%20March%2024%20that%20his%20administration%20would%20be%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-satisfied-doge-cuts-two-to-three-months-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epretty%20much%20satisfied%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20with%20DOGE's%20cuts%20over%20the%20next%20two%20or%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20added%20that%20he%20only%20wanted%20to%20retain%20federal%20workers%20who%20are%20%26quot%3Bhardworking%20and%20want%20to%20be%20members%20of%20the%20administration%20and%20our%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20keep%20the%20good%20ones%2C%20and%20we%20want%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20ones%20that%20don't%20exist%2C%20and%20we%20want%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20ones%20that%20do%20exist%20but%20don't%20work%2C%20and%20we%20have%20quite%20a%20few%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%2C%20DOGE%2C%20Cavanaug