in%20a%20simple%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Raj%20Dhamodharan%2C%20Mastercard's%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20blockchain%20and%20digital%20assets%2C%20said%20of%20traditional%20finance%20and%20decentralized%20finance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20missing%20in%20this%20is%20a%20fully%20compliant%20framework%20and%20consumer%20experience%20offered%20on%20chain%2C%20like%20how%20you%20do%20Venmo%20and%20Zelle%20today%20in%20the%20US%20domestically%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225261%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Raj%20Dhamodharan%2C%20Mastercard's%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20blockchain%20and%20digital%20assets%2C%20standing%20in%20an%20empty%20office%20space.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eaf78c69253ccddf9acf5c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223946%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERaj%20Dhamodharan%2C%20Mastercard's%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20blockchain%20and%20digital%20assets.%3Cp%3EMastercard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBringing%20a%20Venmo-like%20experience%20to%20moving%20money%20and%20other%20assets%20via%20blockchain%20won't%20be%20easy%2C%20and%20financial%20institution%20adoption%20will%20be%20critical.%20As%20with%20any%20network%2C%20the%20value%20of%20the%20network%20increases%20as%20more%20users%20join.%20Mastercard%2C%20for%20its%20part%2C%20is%20targeting%20banks%20to%20join%20its%20crypto-focused%20network%2C%20the%20Multi-Token%20Network%2C%20to%20expand%20its%20functionality.%20So%20far%2C%20Mastercard%20has%20made%20in-roads%20with%20JPMorgan%20and%20Standard%20Chartered%20to%20develop%20new%20use%20cases%2C%20like%20cross-border%20payments%20and%20tokenizing%20deposits%20and%20carbon%20credits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20players%20in%20the%20traditional%20financial%20world%20are%20interested%20in%20moving%20into%20this%20base%20because%20of%20the%20benefits%20the%20technology%20offers%20and%20the%20new%20business%20models%20it%20can%20create%2C%26quot%3B%20Dhamodharan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22295fcbfe-d45e-494b-95ee-f4fc7c1b8d7d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20two-pronged%20crypto%20playbook%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20consumers%2C%20the%20payments%20giant%20wants%20to%20enable%20its%203.5%20billion%20cardholders%20worldwide%20to%20move%20money%20and%20transact%20between%20the%20fiat%20and%20crypto%20worlds.%20Mastercard%20has%20introduced%20more%20than%20100%20different%20crypto-focused%20card%20programs%20globally%2C%20such%20as%20credit%20cards%2C%20prepaid%20cards%2C%20and%20rewards%20cards%2C%20where%20users%20get%20crypto%20instead%20of%20cashback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20flow%20of%20capital%20and%20spending%20power%20from%20the%20consumer%20side%20is%20essential%20to%20the%20success%20of%20this%20entire%20sector%2C%26quot%3B%20Dhamodharan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETraditional%20Wall%20Street%20firms%20represent%20another%20opportunity%20for%20Mastercard%2C%20especially%20as%20real-world%20assets%20increasingly%20become%20tokenized%20or%20represented%20digitally%20on%20blockchain.%20Dhamodharan%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20provide%20a%20way%20to%20process%20blockchain-based%20transactions%20for%20trade%20finance%20and%20cross-border%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDigital%20assets%2C%20such%20as%20cryptocurrencies%2C%20NFTs%2C%20and%20tokenized%20assets%2C%20require%20a%20different%20set%20of%20back-end%20tooling%20than%20traditional%20assets.%20Digital%20assets%20use%20a%20decentralized%2C%20public%20ledger%20that%20sits%20across%20a%20network%20rather%20than%20the%20centralized%20private%20ledger%20most%20banks%20use%20to%20keep%20track%20of%20money%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20this%20infrastructure%20disconnect%20and%20regulatory%20uncertainty%20made%20it%20tricky%20for%20traditional%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-b2b-fintechs-for-crypto-blockchain-web3-defi-infrastructure-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20firms%20to%20access%20crypto%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20presented%20business%20opportunities%20in%20custody%2C%20trading%2C%20and%20wealth%20management.%20For%20banks%20and%20asset%20managers%2C%20crypto%20offered%20some%20upside%20in%20round-the-clock%20transaction%20settlements%2C%20simplifying%20the%20escrow%20process%20for%20home%20buyers%20and%20streamlining%20money%20movements%20between%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMastercard%20has%20made%20a%20sizable%20bet%20on%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Dhamodharan%20said%20of%20Mastercard's%20research%20and%20development%20and%20startup-focused%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202015%2C%20the%20payments%20firm%20has%20filed%20more%20than%20250%20unique%20patents%20related%20to%20blockchain%20and%20digital-asset%20technology%2C%20an%20effort%20that%20involves%20filing%20and%20maintenance%20fees%20and%20employing%20specialized%20legal%20and%20R%26amp%3BD%20teams.%20It%20also%20has%20supported%2043%20blockchain%20startups%20since%202021%20through%20its%20startup%20accelerator%20program.%20While%20the%20firm%20declined%20to%20share%20how%20much%20its%20digital-asset%20team%20has%20grown%20over%20the%20years%2C%20it%20is%20growing.%20Mastercard%20has%20eight%20open%20roles%2C%20some%20fetching%20as%20much%20as%20%24348%2C000%20in%20annual%20pay%2C%20geared%20to%20blockchain%20across%20software%20engineering%2C%20product%2C%20legal%2C%20and%20regulatory%20disciplines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221a54a809-da41-435d-8820-bdd601728f1b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuilding%20the%20next%20foundation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMastercard's%20multi-token%20network%2C%20which%20launched%20in%202023%20and%20is%20the%20foundation%20of%20its%20strategy%2C%20will%20enable%20financial%20institutions%20to%20access%20and%20build%20on%20the%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20November%202024%20integration%20with%20JPMorgan's%20blockchain%20business%20unit%20improved%20the%20speed%20of%20settling%20cross