ariffs%2C%26quot%3B%20Connelly%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20former%20chairman%20of%20the%20American%20International%20Automobile%20Dealers%20Association%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20buying%20a%20%2460%2C000%20car%2C%20that%20really%20adds%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20auto%20tariffs%20are%20part%20of%20a%20package%20of%20duties%20that%20Trump%20is%20expected%20to%20implement%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20which%20the%20president%20has%20dubbed%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliberation-day-trump-tariffs-april-2-canada-mexico-imports-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELiberation%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20Other%20imports%20that%20could%20face%20new%20tariffs%20include%20goods%20from%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%2C%20as%20well%20as%20agricultural%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20tariffs%20or%20potential%20tariffs%20that%20Trump%20and%20his%20administration%20have%20discussed%20threaten%20relatively%20low-cost%20items%2C%20such%20as%20bottles%20of%20tequila%20or%20fresh%20salmon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20tariffs%20could%20add%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20to%20the%20price%20of%20cars%2C%20which%20are%20a%20big%20investment%20for%20many%20middle-income%20households.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20folks%20who%20were%20thinking%20of%20buying%20a%20vehicle%20are%20now%20rushing%20to%20buy%20before%20the%20end%20of%20the%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20Charlie%20Chesbrough%2C%20senior%20economist%20at%20Cox%20Automotive%2C%20said%20in%20comments%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20worry%20is%20that%20higher%20prices%20on%20dealers'%20lots%20will%20follow%20the%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20at%20JPMorgan%20estimated%20in%20late%20March%20that%20the%2025%25%20tariff%20could%20add%20nearly%209%25%20to%20the%20average%20retail%20price%20of%20a%20new%20car%20if%20companies%20fully%20passed%20the%20tariff%20to%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tariff%20migh