nt%20Pai.%20The%20word%20Chitra%20katha%20means%20Chitra%20(picture)%20and%20katha%20(story).%20The%20motive%20of%20this%20kind%20of%20publication%20was%20to%20simplify%20complex%20texts%20into%20illustrations%20so%20that%20it%20is%20easy%20to%20consume%20for%20kids.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20it%E2%80%99s%20used%20today%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20series%20is%20considered%20as%20a%20cultural%20phenomenon%20even%20today%20among%20readers.%20It%20is%20available%20online%2C%20as%20books%20and%20on%20digital%20platforms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKalamkari%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20word%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F259480%2Fandhra-pradesh-kalamkari-art-pitchuka-srinivas-new-york-germany%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKalamkari%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%98pen%20w%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F259480%2Fandhra-pradesh-kalamkari-art-pitchuka-srinivas-new-york-germany%2F%5C%22%3Eork%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fa%3E%20This%20style%20of%20art%20is%20found%20in%20the%20textile%20industry%20and%2C%20like%20Amar%20Chitra%20Katha%2C%20Kalamkari%20to%20depicts%20mythology%20and%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIts%20origin%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKalamkari%E2%80%99s%20roots%20date%20back%20to%20around%203000%20years%20ago%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana.%20This%20form%20of%20art%20was%20initially%20used%20by%20musicians%20and%20painters%20to%20narrate%20mythological%20stories%20on%20huge%20canvases.%20These%20canvases%20were%20usually%20found%20in%20temples.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20it%E2%80%99s%20used%20today%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20today%2C%20this%20art%20form%20is%20considered%20a%20top%20pick%20among%20buyers.%20Thanks%20to%20its%20intricate%20designs%20and%20natural%20dyes%2C%20it%20l